   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00214"/><date>19.</date> früh</dateline><salute rend="center">Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Leider rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e ich eben nach <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01458-1"/><rs ref="#pmb682" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Ragusa</hi></rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01458-1"><rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahr</rs> war vom <date>19.</date> bis
                     <date>23. 10. 1904</date> in <rs ref="#pmb265" type="place">Dalmatien</rs>.</note>. Hoffentlich näch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens einmal.</p><p>Deine <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs>, die ich
               herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t grüße,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>oll jedenfalls zu den <rs ref="#pmb27677 #pmb27674 #pmb2972" type="person">Schwe<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern Flöge</rs> gehen <rs ref="#pmb302" type="place">Mariahilfer<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tr. 1</rs> (<hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb303" type="place">Casa <unclear>p</unclear>iccola</rs></hi>), die für die <rs type="person" ref="#pmb13682" subtype="implied">meinige</rs>
               herrlich gearbeitet haben.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/><signed>H.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
